The minister of Youth and Sports Development, Sunday Dare has said football is ‘content Stupid’ insisting that Nigerian Football Leagues cannot thrive without contents. He made this assertion during an inspection tour of the Surulere National Stadium, Lagos currently undergoing rehabilitation.
